    </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Strategy</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Get Burdens on with many of the Nazgúl and Sauron cards.<br />
<br />
Use Called Away to return powerful companions to hand, then use Ancient Enmity and White Arrows to discard them.<br />
<br />
Use Shapes Slowly Advancing to either add tokens, or if they return to hand, get rid of more companions.<br />
<br />
Either kill or corrupt Frodo.<br />
<br />
(If they are using Galadriel you are doomed. If sne is very popular, [as she is in most places] just add more Between Nazgúl and Prey and Enquëa) </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000"> </Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">DeckTech <BR> For the Players, By the Players  <BR>www.decktech.net </FONT></TD></TR></table> 
